# The 12 per-room shots and the mobile/index frames are REGENERATED, not authored:
#   node _audit/2026-07-13-vfix-css/measure.mjs AFTER    (+ sheet.mjs, shot_ix.mjs)
# They stay on disk for review but out of git. .gitignore at the repo root records why:
# earlier branches committed multi-MB PNG screenshots and the bloat had to be excised.
# What IS committed is the part that cannot be regenerated by looking at a picture -- the
# harness, the numbers it produced, and the two CONTACT SHEETS, which carry all 12
# room-themes between them and are the artifact a reviewer actually needs to look at.
shots/*
!shots/AFTER_SHEET_light.png
!shots/AFTER_SHEET_dark.png
!shots/AFTER_reducedmotion.png
